{"tid":566671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人財兩失?]【銀行拒估值】蔡若蓮擎天半島「凶宅」租2.9萬 低市價兩成","createTime":"2018-02-20T06:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T11:41:04.000Z","uid":51271,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"64e035d1be99acf4c63747ae3991ed3bfa30fa74","tid":566671,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180220/57853337?_ga=2.183754213.219549823.1519085774-486592774.1489390115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57853337%3F_ga%3D2.183754213.219549823.1519085774-486592774.1489390115&d=BIV5xndJp99C8eXOj408iHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=44e78cb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57853337%3F_ga%3D2.183754213.219549823.1519085774-486592774.1489390115&h=87473b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180220/57853337?_ga=2.183754213.219549823.1519085774-486592774.1489390115</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 市場消息透露，尖沙嘴擎天半島3座中層G室「凶宅」，實用面積781方呎，三房間隔，上月以2.9萬元租出，呎租37.1元，較市價約3.7萬元低逾兩成。<br />\n<br />\n單位業主為教育局副局長蔡若蓮，2004年以440萬元買入單位﹔蔡的25歲長子潘匡仁，去年9月被發現於擎天半島41樓住所疑因抑鬱企圖跳樓，被印傭阻止後反鎖房間，印傭致電通知事主父親，豈料他已在房間攀窗躍下倒卧9樓平台，送院不治。本報到滙豐及恒生銀行的網上估值系統嘗試為該單位進行估值，可能因單位曾發生事故，兩間銀行都未能提供估值，而樓下40樓G室，恒生則估值2,120萬元。"},{"pid":"236b1b6d1a19e86a763124c3213fe5bcc53e37d1","tid":566671,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17bcbbeddab74345363be6abfd37cd97fbc77747","tid":566671,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src